        "authorId" : "fb116aef-1bf2-4605-9639-255437a2e564",
        "body" : "Since they appear in the API (which means the user can / must use them for `async0`), and there's no harm in exposing them, I think it's better to make them public.\r\n\r\nWe could hide them with a `fold` method on `Async` that exposes both cases. There's an argument for doing that for performance reasons because then we can avoid allocating the `Now` wrapper.",
